thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FcttWDoFhUiiWqL6d7f%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2d3ff6a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">欅坂46(Keyakizaka46)是日本大型女子偶像組合乃木坂46的姐妹組合</span>，製作人同樣為秋元康。組合名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。2016年4月6日，欅坂46出道單曲《サイレントマジョリティー》販售，首週銷量達261,580枚，除了登上Oricon週榜首位，還同時刷新歷代女性藝人銷量最高的出道單曲。2016年12月31日，出道不足一年即登場NHK紅白歌合戰。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.keyakizaka46.com/img/14/diar/88/mem/member/sub-member-6897_jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.keyakizaka46.com%2Fimg%2F14%2Fdiar%2F88%2Fmem%2Fmember%2Fsub-member-6897_jpg.jpg&h=c3ef22e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.keyakizaka46.com/files/14/diary/k46/member/moblog/201807/mob4wEGI2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.keyakizaka46.com%2Ffiles%2F14%2Fdiary%2Fk46%2Fmember%2Fmoblog%2F201807%2Fmob4wEGI2.jpg&h=801bf1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成員名單</span></span><br />\n<br />\n欅坂46<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/041026_adc5e7302d752f990a849cbbcd1daa06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F041026_adc5e7302d752f990a849cbbcd1daa06.png&h=35d10a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/041030_acacab65df3e227410b279bf1a62837a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F041030_acacab65df3e227410b279bf1a62837a.png&h=43e5ce25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nけやき坂46 (ひらがなけやき)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hBNnhH3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhBNnhH3.png&h=f2073abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nけやき坂46 (ひらがなけやき)2期生<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iJfveqb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiJfveqb.png&h=d1e38e4e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.keyakizaka46.com/images/14/ca4/7df966cb2b68774ba8a03a3631fcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.keyakizaka46.com%2Fimages%2F14%2Fca4%2F7df966cb2b68774ba8a03a3631fcc.jpg&h=eb484400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">欅坂46 7thシングル 「アンビバレント」好評発売中!!!</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://cdn.keyakizaka46.com/images/14/8e5/88115dfa4ec0bc65f7a462bc96a6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.keyakizaka46.com%2Fimages%2F14%2F8e5%2F88115dfa4ec0bc65f7a462bc96a6a.jpg&h=2a693ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">けやき坂46(ひらがなけやき)1stアルバム 「走り出す瞬間」 好評発売中!!</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n【我老婆有幾靚女？】我直接用例子答你。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/124925_547811e16fc96b0b226625d207bf9114.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F124925_547811e16fc96b0b226625d207bf9114.png&h=68d077a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/124930_6f0a74129b2a663609eb0e360a28565d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F124930_6f0a74129b2a663609eb0e360a28565d.png&h=c16fe38a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/124938_c62d31f9c9bdada2641687cc95b2037a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F124938_c62d31f9c9bdada2641687cc95b2037a.png&h=6fb06cfd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/124947_cda74cf12e813162f44f2c6cc530